OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Mon 20 Apr to Wed 29 Apr
OL,6,FHigh pressure to the north or
OL,7,Fnortheast of the UK will bring plenty
OL,8,Fof dry weather and sunny spells for
OL,9,Fmost at first. Low pressure in the
OL,10,FAtlantic will try to push weather
OL,11,Ffronts towards the UK from the south
OL,12,Fwest, but these may remain slow
OL,13,Fmoving. Some parts of the east coast
OL,14,Fcould be on the chilly side with low
OL,15,Fcloud and onshore breeze, but further
OL,16,Fwest it will likely feel quite warm,
OL,17,Fespecially in sunnier areas. From next
OL,18,Fweekend and into the start of the
OL,19,Ffollowing week, there are signs that
OL,20,Fmore unsettled weather could return
OL,21,Ffor a time, bringing rain or showers
OL,22,Fto some areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,164,160,301,260,100,100
PN,16303
