CT,20,T
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1776262271
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G3/3
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wed 29 Apr to Wed 13 May
OL,6,FThe dominant pattern during this
OL,7,Fperiod is most likely to be high
OL,8,Fpressure (or higher than average
OL,9,Fpressure) to the north and lower
OL,10,Fpressure to the south. This will
OL,11,Fprobably lead to drier and more
OL,12,Fsettled than normal weather in the
OL,13,Fnorth or northwest of the UK, with the
OL,14,Fsouth and southwest likely seeing a
OL,15,Fgreater chance of some rain at times.
OL,16,FTemperatures will probably be close to
OL,17,For slightly above average overall,
OL,18,Fperhaps becoming more widely warm at
OL,19,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
